---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Story | YourHQ - Infrastructure + Warmth" 
  description="Founded by Lian in Whangārei. Combining high-tech infrastructure with Pacific warmth."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-paper min-h-screen">
    
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-24 border-b border-carbon bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-12">
            Infrastructure <br/>
            <span class="text-frangipani">& Warmth.</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="max-w-2xl border-l-4 border-carbon pl-8 py-2">
            <p class="text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed">
                We bridge the gap between Silicon Valley tech and Pacific hospitality. Between code and conversation.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

   <!-- THE ORIGIN -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                
     <!-- ... inside the grid ... -->

<!-- LEFT SIDE -->
<div class="md:col-span-5">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-8">The 15-Year Timeline</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="transform -rotate-2 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-1.png" alt="Lian" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div class="transform rotate-2 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-5.png" alt="Whangarei" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div class="transform rotate-1 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-3.png" alt="Dinner and ideas" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div class="transform -rotate-1 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-4.png" alt="Early days" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- RIGHT SIDE -->
<div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-8 text-lg text-carbon/80 leading-relaxed pt-8">
    <div class="md:hidden mb-8">
        <!-- Mobile-only image -->
        <img src="/us-3.png" class="w-full border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard" alt="Lian" />
    </div>

    <p>
        I've always had a passion for <strong>Storytelling</strong> and empowering small businesses.
    </p>
    <p>
        While having coffee in Whangārei, I realized something troubling. So many of the local businesses I loved were digitally homeless. The builders, the bakers, the tradies who've been around for 20 years.
    </p>
    <p>
        They were living entirely on Facebook or Instagram — vulnerable to algorithms they couldn't control.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-carbon my-8 shadow-hard-sm relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-6 bg-frangipani/80 rotate-1"></div>
        <p class="font-bold text-xl text-carbon mb-2">I thought: This isn't right.</p>
        <p>It's time for business owners to stop being tenants and start being owners.</p>
    </div>

    <p>
        So I decided to build something about it.
    </p>
</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE FOUNDER -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

                <!-- Lian -->
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
                    <div class="md:col-span-2">
                        <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon mb-8 relative overflow-hidden">
                            <img src="/lian-headshot.png" alt="Lian Passmore" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-3">
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">Lian</h3>
                        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-signal font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Founder</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                            I bring both the tech and the heart. With a background in automation and AI, I ensure the infrastructure runs with precision while keeping every client relationship personal and warm.
                        </p>

                        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">My Story:</p>
                                <p>Grew up watching my dad run a small business — brilliant at the work, frustrated by the admin. I married someone in the trades. Same story. While studying technological futures and data sovereignty, I kept thinking: <em>Why aren't we building tools for people like my dad? Like my husband?</em> That became my mission: <strong>Use cutting-edge tech to empower everyday business owners.</strong></p>
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">What I Believe:</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                    <li>• Strong infrastructure is the highest form of care</li>
                                    <li>• Technology should empower, not confuse</li>
                                    <li>• Small businesses deserve Silicon Valley tools</li>
                                    <li>• If it can be automated, it should be</li>
                                    <li>• You should own your digital space, not rent it</li>
                                    <li>• Every business has a story worth telling</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                            <div>
                                <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">Background:</p>
                                <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                    <li>• Studied technological futures & data sovereignty</li>
                                    <li>• Deep passion for SMEs (grew up around small business)</li>
                                    <li>• Builds AI agents & automation systems</li>
                                    <li>• Uses Astro + Tailwind CSS for high-performance sites</li>
                                    <li>• Pacific heritage with Cook Island roots</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                            <div class="pt-2">
                                <p class="font-bold text-carbon">My Specialty:</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">AI voice agents (the Digital Twin), automation systems, and Silicon Valley infrastructure with real-world empathy. Making your website feel authentically like <em>you</em>, while giving you time back.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PACIFIC ROOTS -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-paper">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8">Born from the Pacific.</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-12">
                    Like many Pacific people raised in Aotearoa, I grew up disconnected from my heritage language but deeply connected to the values: <strong>Service, Respect, and Stewardship.</strong>
                </p>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                    <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <strong class="block text-frangipani mb-2 text-lg">Ownership</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">You own the house. No landlords.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <strong class="block text-hibiscus mb-2 text-lg">Stewardship</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">I care for it, but I don't hold it hostage.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <strong class="block text-signal mb-2 text-lg">Respect</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Tech should serve you, not confuse you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-300 mt-12 font-medium">
                    These aren't borrowed concepts. They're how I was raised to do business.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>